        <tr><td>Door gasket replacement</td><td>$220 – $400</td><td>Undercounter profile, U-Line channel</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Combo drawer slide service</td><td>$300 – $600</td><td>2 Class and 3 Class combo configurations</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Condenser fan motor replacement</td><td>$260 – $440</td><td>Standard U-Line specs on truck</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Evaporator fan motor replacement</td><td>$240 – $400</td><td>7–10 year common service</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Defrost heater / thermostat</td><td>$280 – $480</td><td>Defrost cycle repair</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Compressor capacitor / starter relay</td><td>$180 – $280</td><td>10–14 year common service</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Main control board replacement</td><td>$440 – $720</td><td>Post-diagnosis</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Compressor replacement (post-warranty)</td><td>$900 – $1,600</td><td>Uncommon before year 12</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Outdoor unit service premium</td><td>+$40 – $80 labor</td><td>Access + environmental factors</td></tr>
      </table>
      <p class="small">
        Broader refrigerator cost reference: our <a href="/price-list/refrigerator-repair-cost/">refrigerator repair
        cost guide</a>. Wine-specific context: <a href="/services/wine-cooler-repair/">wine cooler repair</a>.
        Built-in-specific scope: <a href="/services/built-in-refrigerator-repair/">built-in refrigerator repair</a>.
        U-Line hub: <a href="/brands/u-line/">U-Line brand hub</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>Service areas, where our U-Line calls come from</h2>
      <div class="area-grid">
        <div>
          <h4>Westside (home-bar + butler's pantry installs)</h4>
          <p><a href="/beverly-hills/">Beverly Hills</a> · Bel Air · <a href="/brentwood/">Brentwood</a> · <a href="/pacific-palisades/">Pacific Palisades</a> · <a href="/santa-monica/">Santa Monica</a></p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Coastal + outdoor-rated U-Line</h4>
          <p><a href="/malibu/">Malibu</a> · Venice · Manhattan Beach · Palos Verdes · Newport Coast · Newport Beach</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Hidden Hills + custom entertaining kitchens</h4>
          <p>Hidden Hills · Calabasas · <a href="/encino/">Encino</a> · Sherman Oaks · Tarzana</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Hollywood Hills + modernist</h4>
          <p>Hollywood Hills · Laurel Canyon · Nichols Canyon · Mount Olympus · Outpost Estates</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>San Gabriel Valley</h4>
          <p><a href="/pasadena/">Pasadena</a> · San Marino · South Pasadena · La Cañada · Arcadia</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Ventura + Orange County</h4>
          <p><a href="/thousand-oaks/">Thousand Oaks</a> · Westlake Village · Laguna Beach · Irvine · Coto de Caza</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
